Then 
\begin_inset Formula $P\{(\limsup A_{n}\Delta\{\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}P(A_{n}|\mathcal{F}_{n-1})=\infty\}\}=0$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta$
\end_inset

stands for the symmetric difference.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Proof: 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "R. J. Serfling, 1975"

\end_inset

