\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
Definition:
\series default
 A sequence of random variables 
\begin_inset Formula ${X_{n};n≥1}$
\end_inset

 is said to be pairwise negative quadrant dependent (NQD) if, 
\begin_inset Formula $P(X_{i}\leq x,Y_{j}\leq y)\leq P(X_{i}\leq x)P(Y_{j}\leq y)$
\end_inset

 For all 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y\in R$
\end_inset

 and for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i,j≥1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $i\text{≠}j$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

